INSERT INTO admin_users (
                uuid, path, username, email, password_hash, first_name, last_name,
                is_active, created_at, updated_at, published, version, 
                created_by
            ) VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, 
                $8, $9, $9, $10, 1, 
                $11
            ) RETURNING uuid
